Author: ChubbieToad
Text: That sounds like a nightmare. I hope it gets better for you. One day at a time.

Author: zombeezinthetrap
Text: I relate to this soo much. Before treatment, I told myself and my friends I didn’t care about weight. I was trying to gain weight but I just kept losing because I wasn’t feeding myself. When I entered treatment and had a breakdown the first day because I was so bloated I looked pregnant, I was like hmmm maybe I do have an eating disorder lmao.
